name: Enhanced TIE Laser Cannon
Lore: 'Sienar Fleet Systems'' latest laser cannon prototype increases the firepower most Imperial TIEs - but many Moffs consider the weapon too expensive for widespread use.',
Text: 'Use 1 Force to deploy on your TIE. May target a starship using 1 Force. Draw destiny. Subtract 2 if targeting a capital starship. Target hit if destiny > defense value.',
